 * images.image_1_desktop => 卡片1桌面图片:textarea:|留空则不显示图片
 * images.image_1_mobile => 卡片1移动端图片:textarea:|留空则不显示图片
 *
 * group:game_2 => 卡片2配置
 * texts.game_2_badge => 卡片2徽章:text:Fast Queue
 * texts.game_2_title => 卡片2标题:text:Smart Table
 * texts.game_2_desc => 卡片2描述:textarea:Balanced room with cleaner spacing for repeat sessions.
 * texts.game_2_tag => 卡片2标签:text:Balanced Tempo
 * texts.game_2_url => 卡片2链接:text:#smart
 * images.image_2 => 卡片2图片:textarea:|留空则不显示图片
 *
 * group:game_3 => 卡片3配置
 * texts.game_3_badge => 卡片3徽章:text:Player Favorite
 * texts.game_3_title => 卡片3标题:text:Focus Room
 * texts.game_3_desc => 卡片3描述:textarea:Lower-noise layout for players who prefer measured decisions.
 * texts.game_3_tag => 卡片3标签:text:Late Night Sessions
 * texts.game_3_url => 卡片3链接:text:#focus
 * images.image_3 => 卡片3图片:textarea:|留空则不显示图片
 *
 * group:game_4 => 卡片4配置
