 * texts.game_4_title => 卡片4标题:text:Night Rally
 * texts.game_4_desc => 卡片4描述:textarea:Late-session room tuned for sustained play.
 * texts.game_4_tag => 卡片4标签:text:Quick Entry
 * texts.game_4_url => 卡片4链接:text:#night
 *
 * group:game_5 => 卡片5配置
 * texts.game_5_badge => 卡片5徽章:text:New User
 * texts.game_5_title => 卡片5标题:text:Prime Gin
 * texts.game_5_desc => 卡片5描述:textarea:Flagship room with bold visuals and priority queue.
 * texts.game_5_tag => 卡片5标签:text:Balanced Tempo
 * texts.game_5_url => 卡片5链接:text:#prime
 *
 * @fields_end
